data.description: Step inside this lovely Palm Desert Country Club home and enjoy the sweeping views of the backyard pool and greenbelt beyond. The property was thoughtfully updated in 2016 with new granite countertops, new stainless steel appliances, dual pane windows and sliders as well as vinyl plank flooring. In the last 2 years, the pool pump has been replaced as well as the water heater. New ceiling fans have been installed and electrical outlets and switches have been updated. The best part is that the home has 24 OWNED SOLAR PANELS! No more outrageous summer electricity costs! The bonus room off the kitchen makes a fantastic office space and the attached, interior laundry is removed enough from the living space that it doesn't add any additional heat during a dryer cycle! Enjoy the sweeping mountain views from the backyard and spend those hot summer days in your large, private pool! This home is warm, welcoming and perfect for a full tine residence or desert retreat.
